Widgit's Privacy Policy
Widgit takes privacy very seriously, that's why your information will only be used for displaying on your widgets. You can enable or disable the app's permissions at any time from the iOS Settings app.
â€‹
Please see below for details:
Location
Your location will only be used for displaying local weather information on your widgets.
Calendar and Photos
Your calendar information and photos will only be used for displaying on your widgets.
Health
Your health information will only be used for displaying Activity Data on your widgets.
